.DT
soul
$MUDNAME$ player help
soul

.SH Name
.SI 5
soul - The wonderful feelings thing.
.EI

.SH Pinkfish's soul.

.SH How to use (What can it do for you?):
.SP 5 5
The feeling or atmosphere commands that you use, like smile and so
on come from your soul.  The soul used on this mud is different to most
others you will have come across.  Below are a few examples of what you
can do with this soul.
.EP

.SI 5
> smile happily at Shiannar
You smile happily at Shiannar.
> smile w at Shiannar
You smile wryly at Shiannar
> shake hands with Shiannar
You shake hands with Shiannar
> shake hands Shiannar
You shake hands with Shiannar.
.EI

.SP 5 5
The above are a few examples of what can be done with the soul.  The usage
of the command (i.e. whether you use and at or a with or whatever... well,
just use what seems right... It should work).  To see what soul commands are
available to you at any given time type 'souls'.
.EP

.SI 5
> souls
The number of soul commands currently available is 489.
Here is a nice list of them.
Good luck!
absolve      cough        grate        nod          shake        swoon
<complete list of souls omitted in this helpfile>
.EI

.SP 5 5
To find all the possible parameters for a given soul command, type 'help <soul>'
.EP

.SI 5
> help shake
Allowed command patterns:
shake <string> [with|at] <indirect:any-living>
<complete help file omitted in this helpfile>
.EI

.SP 5 5
Most of the soul commands can be either targetted or untargetted,
plus you can specify additional arguments.
.EP

.SI 5
> shake l
You shake your leg.
> shake arm
You shake your arm.
>shake hand avelan
womble greenly avelan
You womble around Assistant Avelan Al'Jabr greenly.

.EI

.SP 5 5
Womble on.
.EP


.SH Idea reporting souls

.SP 5 5
If you find a missing command use the following command to get it added by
someone who can.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SP 5 5
idea soul
.EP

.SH Examples
.SI 5
idea soul bleed
 - I want to be able to bleed on people.

idea soul kick
- I keep typing kick Liceas and it fails!

idea soul snicker

idea soul smile
smile spasmodically would be cute
.EI

.SH See also
.SI 5
alias, help, history.
.EI
